{"about_the_game":"Rocking Legend is a musical game where you'll take the part of a virtual rock star immersed in beautiful and dynamic environments.<br><br>Choose between <strong>guitar</strong> or <strong>drums</strong> and immediately go on stage in <strong>free-play</strong> mode. Alternatively, you can participate in the single-player <strong>campaign</strong> through a series of levels and original soundtracks created purposely for the game to improve your skills and unlock <strong>new instrument skins</strong>. If you don't want to play alone, you can even play in <strong>multiplayer</strong> PvP or cooperatively in a band of two!<br><br>Compete on the global <strong>leaderboards</strong> using your preferred control scheme and a selection of <strong>gameplay modifiers</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Guitar modes:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Finger-tracked</strong> (only index controllers at the moment)<br></li><li> <strong>Hand-tracked</strong> with two sub-modes: Classic or Advanced<br></li><li> <strong>PC Keyboard / Game controllers support</strong></li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260800/extras/FingerGif.gif?t=1726308202\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260800/extras/HandGif.gif?t=1726308202\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260800/extras/NewHandPlaystyle.gif?t=1726308202\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260800/extras/GameDevices480x270.jpg?t=1726308202\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Drums features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play with the virtual drum set<br></li><li> Adjust the height and position for each drum piece<br></li><li> Two notes visualization modes: on-piece or in-line<br></li><li> Optional drum-kick<br></li><li> PC Keyboard / Game controllers support</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260800/extras/DrumGif2.gif?t=1726308202\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay modifiers:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Note speed multiplier<br></li><li> Song playback speed<br></li><li> Random dynamic lane speed<br></li><li> Bomb notes<br></li><li> Lane changing notes<br></li><li> Invisible notes<br></li><li> Automatic plectrum<br></li><li> and more!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tracklist:</h2><br>The game ships with <strong>18 original songs</strong> explicitly created for the game, charted in multiple levels, grouped by instrument type, and available on various difficulty levels. You can also play <strong>custom songs</strong> made with external tools.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Three game modes:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Campaign</strong>: learn the fundamentals and improve your skills through a series of increasingly challenging levels, while unlocking new instrument skins<br></li><li> <strong>Free play</strong>: customize your experience and compete on the global leaderboards<br></li><li> <strong>Multiplayer</strong>: play in a band of two in coop mode or compete in VS for the highest score</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beginner guitarist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1260800/09343cbbcd3da561e5977a244471a0cad2a51b62.jpg"},{"name":"Beginner drummer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1260800/dba14ed84f8ce2459ce18746d073f37308cc64e5.jpg"},{"name":"Apprentice guitarist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1260800/860ac446c0d9a2eede48a5ec8a8919d58feb37e6.jpg"},{"name":"Apprentice drummer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1260800/847e885235749099e48d79b9054a7b8fc4c0e8a6.jpg"},{"name":"Advanced guitarist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcom